p: \bMr. Zenith, sir, the kid you asked to see is here.
\bMa'am, I'm very sorry about this, but it's very likely you've contracted the virus.
\bMa'am, you were caught trying to avoid my team to avoid vaccination.
\bThat's very suspicious behaviour. There's really only one possibility.
\bI'm afraid you'll have to be quarantined. It's for the good of the region.
\rBut... you're going to vaccinate me! I won't have the virus anymore!
\bI'm very sorry ma'am. We just can't take any risks.
\bHowever... if there's anyone else you know who is in hiding...
\bPerhaps we can come to some sort of arrangement?
\rOh yes. I can help you, please don't send me away.
\bThat sounds wonderful. Thank you, Mrs. Williams, you're doing your region a service.
\bJust report to my friend at the front desk.\nGet your shot, give him info, and I'm sure we can help you stay safe.
\b\pn, are you familiar with the witch trials?
\bThey were a long, long time ago, and since the Augur's rewritten most of the history books, I wouldn't be surprised if you're not.
\bThe story stars a young little girl who wanted to learn witchcraft.
\bTo avoid getting trouble for it, she accused other townsfolk of being witches.
\bThose who didn't confess were hanged. Those who did, and accused others, were allowed to live.
\bThe town was a mess within a month. Accusations ran rampant.
\bEveryone threw their friends and family under the bus to save their hides.
\bIt's not very heartwarming, but it works for me.
\bIt's a very common strategy amongst dictators and tyrants.
\bLetting people off the hook as long as they turn others in.
\bThey do the work for you, and it works beautifully well.
\bI don't know exactly how this virus works or where it came from, but I'm definitely going to capitalize on its existence.
\bI think I'm done here. I didn't call you in here to monologue.
\bI called you in here to show you exactly why you should be terrified of my cult.
\bGood. We're done here. Stall her while we leave, please.
\bGood. We're done here. Stall him while we leave, please.
\bI guess it's hard to tell the difference, considering how empty and brainwashed the people of this region already are...
\b...but anyways. I'm in a hurry. Have fun, you two.
\rYou must be stalled. Zenith has commanded it.
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::MEDIUM,"A. Williams",_I("...I... what? What's going on?!"),false,0)
